    fix: use permanent message handler and firstDataRequest for reliable candle loading
    
    - Replace per-batch onmessage swapping with a permanent handler + closure resolver
    - Set firstDataRequest: true for batch 0 (NXOS protocol requirement)
    - Install onmessage before SUBSCRIBE so no server messages are dropped
    - Single historyResolver variable ensures one pending request at a time
    
